R.VALUE
=======
* Bug fix in annual spellmax computation
* New argument 'n.mem' in validation wrapper to control the number of realizations to be computed.
* New argument 'threshold.type' in spell indices to indicate quantile-based thresholds in addition to absolute.
* Enhancement in the internal 'getIntersect' in order to handle unsorted time series prior to validation.
* Other minor documentation updates and improvements.




